Name: Base Station, Ano Dos Mil Car & Limo Servoce, Brppklyn
Title: A Local Law in relation to the approval of a determination by the Taxi and Limousine Commission to approve an application by Ano Dos Mil Car and Limousine Service also known as Ano Dos Mil Car & Limo Service and also known as Ano Dos Mil Car & Limo. Svc. for a license to operate a new base station in the borough of Brooklyn.
Text:
Be it enacted by the Council as follows:

      Section one.  The determination by the Taxi and Limousine Commission to approve an application by Ano Dos Mil Car and Limousine Service also known as Ano Dos Mil Car & Limo Service and also known as Ano Dos Mil Car & Limo. Svc. for a license to operate a new base station at 211 South First Street in the borough of Brooklyn is hereby approved. 
      ï¿½2. This local law shall take effect immediately. 

LS#2001
7/14/1999
